text: left Zuidzande is a village in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Sluis. Zuidzande was a separate municipality until 1970, when it was merged with Oostburg.Ad van der Meer and Onno Boonstra, "Repertorium van Nederlandse gemeenten", KNAW, 2006. ==References== ==External links== *Map of the former municipality in 1868 Category:Populated places in Zeeland Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Sluis
